=== |A_d| ANALYSIS ===
For p ≡ 3 mod 4: -1 is NQR, so -QR = NQR.
A_2 = m * m = m² (since s_2 = -s_1 is NQR, always allowed)
  P_7: A_2 = 9, m² = 9. Match: True
  P_11: A_2 = 25, m² = 25. Match: True

A_3 formula: m(m-1)(2m+1)/2
  P_7: A_3 = 21, predicted = 21. Match: True
  P_11: A_3 = 110, predicted = 110. Match: True

